Current Investigations 






Zamansky LLC Investigates the Visium Credit Opportunities Hedge Fund
March 14, 2016



Zamansky LLC is investigating the collapse of the Visium Credit Opportunities Fund LP and Offshore Fund Ltd., the $280 million hedge fund which shut in 2013. On March 6, 2016, Visium Asset Management LP reportedly sent a letter to investors notifying them that the U.S. Department of Justice and S.E.C. are investigating the way the hedge funds valued and traded certain assets, and its use of a consultant.
If you were an investor in the Visium Credit Opportunities hedge funds and suffered a loss when it shut, please contact our firm for an evaluation of your rights. You can contact Jake Zamansky by telephone at (212) 742-1414 or by email at jake@zamansky.com.





